- Consider homerow mods, but only while the left thumb key is pressed.
    - Only for Ctrl and Alt. Shift is unnecesary.

- Consider a way of toggling the num pad with the right hand.
    - Not hold, but toggle.

- Allow Enter with ñ+k on all layers, not just the default one.
    - This is to allow using it on the symbols or mumbers layer.
    - Maybe using a combo?

- Numbers with alt (left hand).
    - Or maybe just use software for this.
        - Same with Control.
        - Not the idea, though.

- Modal movement layer.
    - Add deletion sub-layer
    - Add selection sub-layer
